---

<h3>LeetCode Stats</h3>
<div
	class="flex flex-wrap justify-evenly border border-border ~gap-2/4 ~rounded-none/xl ~p-2/4"
>
	<span>Rank: <strong>{leetcode.matchedUser.profile?.ranking}</strong></span>
	<span>
		Solved: <strong>
			{leetcode.completedCount.total} ({leetcode.completedPercentage.total})
		</strong>
	</span>
	<span
		>Rating: <strong>{leetcode.matchedUser.profile?.starRating}</strong></span
	>
</div>
